title: #19 one note, one post
body:
I personally find all Pokemon LINE stickers really cute - I just wanted to proclaim my love for their most recent collection because it is stupidly adorable and funny: 

Project Eevee - ぷろじぇくといーぶい stickers! Kudos for the artist conveying a variety of… very specific emotions in such charming illustrations.

(one note, one post project)

summary: I do want to point out that Meltan and Melmetal possess the “simplistic” design style that Game Freak stated that they wanted to...
body:
I do want to point out that Meltan and Melmetal possess the “simplistic” design style that Game Freak stated that they wanted to roll back to during interviews in the Gen 6 era. The designs are simple, but they posses a striking centerpiece that defines what they are and what their purpose/influence is.

I have confidence that I will enjoy the Gen 8 designs if they follow the same level of relative minimalism.
